title: How to Grow Through Suffering
itunes:title: How to Grow Through Suffering
description:
Will Smith and some of the most successful people in the world have changed their lives through a concept called "applied suffering." While most people run from suffering, the most successful people in the world run towards suffering. In this episode, I am going to teach you how to use suffering to get the life you want.
